# This repo currently does not read any runtime environment variables.
#
# Frontend:
# - API base is hard-coded to `/api/v1` in `frontend/src/api/client.ts`
# - WebSocket base is derived from the browser location in
#   `frontend/src/hooks/useCollaborativeDoc.ts`
# - Vite dev proxy targets are hard-coded in `frontend/vite.config.ts`
#
# Backend:
# - Host/port are set by the `uvicorn` command in `Makefile`
# - CORS origin is hard-coded in `backend/app/main.py`
# - AI uses the in-repo `EchoAIProvider` and does not read an external API key
